ass=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 17, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tmv1665702775850.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tmv1665702775850.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tmv1665702775850.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tmv1665702775850\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Instructs the Uniface Server to keep every UAR or ZIP archive that it reads open until\n      the Uniface Server itself shuts down. Applicable only in deployment environments.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tmv1665702775850__topic_d143846e1_d143847e1_d143848e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tmv1665702775850__p_d143849e1_d143850e1_d143851e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ZIP_KEEPOPEN</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tmv1665702775850__section_jkb_wzm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d636337e58\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tmv1665702775850__p_d143855e1_d143856e1_d143857e1\">This setting can only be used in deployment\n            environments, and only with Uniface Servers that never write to a UAR or ZIP files.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tmv1665702775850__p_d143858e1_d143859e1_d143860e1\">Do not use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ZIP_KEEPOPEN</span> in a\n            development environment or in an environment where the Uniface Server writes to UAR or\n            ZIP files. If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ZIP_KEEPOPEN</span> is used in a development environment,\n            errors may occur in the IDE because target UARs are locked by a Uniface Server.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tmv1665702775850__p_d143861e1_d143862e1_d143863e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ZIP_KEEPOPEN</span> makes it faster to\n            access remote resources. You can improve performance further by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$MEMORY\n               ZIP</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=all</code>, which maps archives into memory.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/krm1665702718866.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$MEMORY</a><p>Control memory allocation for Uniface application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532429\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532429\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$ZIP_KEEPOPEN Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 17, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Instructs the Uniface Server to keep every UAR or ZIP archive that it reads open until the Uniface Server itself shuts down. Applicable only in deployment environments. $ZIP_KEEPOPEN Description This setting can only be used in deployment environments, and only with Uniface Servers that never write to a UAR or ZIP files. Do not use $ZIP_KEEPOPEN in a development environment or in an environment where the Uniface Server writes to UAR or ZIP files. If $ZIP_KEEPOPEN is used in a development environment, errors may occur in the IDE because target UARs are locked by a Uniface Server. $ZIP_KEEPOPEN makes it faster to access remote resources. You can improve performance further by setting $MEMORY ZIP =all , which maps archives into memory. Related Links $MEMORY Control memory allocation for Uniface application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}